    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. <date>Temporibus domni
                            nostri viri precellentissimi <persName key="#Princeps"
                                ref="#people/2000">Grimoaldi</persName>, Dei providencia,
                            Beneventane provincie <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>, decimo anno
                            principatus eius, mense septembris, VIIII indictione</date>. Ideoque ego
                            <persName ref="#people/1902">Alahis</persName>, filius bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Arichis">Arichis</name></persName>, pro
                        redepmcione anime mee, per hanc meam <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">chartulam
                            offercionis</rs>, offero in <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1900">Beati Vincencii
                            levite et martyris</orgName>, ubi Deo favente domnus <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/2001">Iosue</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preest, omnes res et substancias meas, quas
                        habeo intus vel foras <rs key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Houses #Curtes #Houses #Rivers" ref="#places/2300"
                            >Benafro</placeName>, hoc est <rs key="#Houses">casas</rs> meas
                        fabrittas, cum suis <rs key="#Curtes">curtibus</rs>, que sunt posite super
                        fontem <rs key="#Rivers">fluvii</rs> qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Mills #Riverbed" ref="#places/2346">Sexto</placeName>;
                        quam et <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> nostram vocabulo <orgName
                            key="#Rivers #Churches #Landed_possessions #Fruits/vegetables"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1920">Sancte Marie</orgName>, que constructa est
                        iuxta ipsum fluvium, cum suo <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fruits/vegetables">ortale</rs>; quam et terras
                        meas quas habeo in <rs key="#Fines">finibus</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Fines #Petiae #Houses #Roads #Riverbed #Rivers #Mountains #Landed_possessions #Mills #Clusae/gates #Churches #Slave #Slave_labour #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/1901">Benafro</geogName>, in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Riverbed #Mountains #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Mills #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Slave_labour #Clusae/gates #Roads #Churches #Slave"
                            ref="#places/2347">Maczano</placeName>, que sunt due pecie: prima <rs
                            key="#Petiae">pecia</rs>, ubi ecclesia vocabulo Sancte Marie constructa
                        est, et <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> fabritta, que in eadem terra posita est,
                        que habet fines iam dicta prima pecia qualiter exfinant <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terre</rs> et <rs key="#Mountains"
                        >montes</rs>, que domnus <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/303"
                            >Arichis</persName>, bone memorie <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>,
                        concessas habet per suum <rs key="#Marquisâ€™/ducal/princely_diploma"
                            >preceptum</rs> in iam dicto monasterio, secunda parte <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >riagine</rs> que dicitur <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/2309"
                            >Ravennola</placeName>, unde per tempus aqua decurrit, tercia parte
                        fossato, et terras <persName><name ref="Iohannes Radoaldus">Iohannis
                                Radoaldi</name></persName>, et terras <persName><name
                                ref="Emelgrimus">Emelgrimi</name></persName>, et terras
                                <persName><name ref="Paldo">Paldoni</name></persName>, et terras
                                <persName><name ref="Truppoaldus">Truppoaldi</name></persName>,
                        quarta vero parte riagine; secunda <rs key="#Petiae">pecia</rs> ibidem, que
                        habet fines: prima parte <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers" ref="#places/609">Vulturno</placeName>, de secunda
                        parte riagine, que exfinat inter hec terra et terra Arichis principis,
                        tercia parte iam dicta riagine, quarta parte fines habet terram
                                <persName><name ref="Medancius">Medanci</name></persName>; quam et
                        offero in iam dicto monasterio inclitum <rs key="#Mills">molendinum</rs>
                        meum, quem habeo in iam dicto fluvio Sexto, cum <rs key="#Clusae/gates"
                            >clusuris</rs>, ripis, aquis, et cum suo <rs key="#Riverbed">cursu</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Roads">viis</rs> ibidem intrandi et exiendi; iterum offero in
                        eodem monasterio <rs key="#Slave #Slave_labour">servos</rs> et ancillas
                        nostras, qui in iam dictis terris habitant, quorum nomina hec sunt:
                            <persName key="#Slave #Slave_labour"><name ref="Theodericus"
                                >Theodericus</name></persName> cum <persName
                            key="#Slave #Slave_labour"><name ref="Pota">Pota</name></persName> uxore
                        sua, <persName key="#Slave #Slave_labour"><name ref="Dominicus"
                                >Dominicus</name></persName> cum <persName
                            key="#Slave #Slave_labour"><name ref="Rosa">Rosa</name></persName> uxore
                        sua, <persName key="#Slave #Slave_labour"><name ref="Ursulus"
                            >Ursulus</name></persName> cum <persName key="#Slave #Slave_labour"
                                ><name ref="Formica">Formica</name></persName> uxore sua, <persName
                            key="#Slave #Slave_labour"><name ref="Petrulus"
                            >Petrulus</name></persName> cum <persName key="#Slave #Slave_labour"
                                ><name ref="Angela">Angela</name></persName> uxore sua, cum filiis,
                        nuribus, nepotibus, et cum omnibus suis cespitibus. Hec omnia in integrum
                        offero ad possidendum eidem monasterio Sancti Vincencii in perpetuum. </ab>
